items.sentence: I told Tom I didn't want to ever see him again.
I know it's hard, but you have to try doing it.
Tom asked me to feed his dog while he was away.
How do you train a dog not to tug on its leash?
Tom is certain that Mary can understand French.
Tom is the only one that knows where Mary went.
Tom is the last person I'd expect to see there.
Tom isn't the only one who knows where Mary is.
I got worried when Tom didn't answer his phone.
Tom realized that Mary wasn't going to do that.
